{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_98","type":"agent_message","text":"The scratch repro clarified one important point on this GraalVM: `java.lang.Object.<init>` can work, but only when the deserialized root type itself is registered in a way native-image actually treats as serializable. I’m making the root credential serialization entries unconditional now, while keeping the more specific leaf registrations as-is."}}
